Ptomaine poisoning ! The name had an ugly sound , and Condy's use of the term inferred the doctor's visit . 
Blix decided that she would put off her walk until the afternoon , and call on Mrs. Rivers at once , and ask how Condy did . 
She got away from the flat about ten o'clock , but on the steps outside met Condy dressed as if for bicycling , and smoking a cigarette . 
I've got eleven dollars ! he announced cheerily . 
